rdebootstrap (0.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * BREAKING CHANGE: the solver now enforces that a child spec 
    cannot drop packages locked by a parent spec. This change 
    allows to enable incremental builds in deb-ostree.
  * BREAKING CHANGE: major and long deserved Manifest API overhaul.
    Move most of spec-querying methods into a first-class 
    ResolvedSpecRef type. Simplify and de-duplicate Manifest API.
  * BREAKING CHANGE: add lock file format versioning.
  * BREAKING CHANGE: more consistent spec hashing scheme. 
  * feat: enable incremental builds.
  * fix: detect and reject duplicate packages with different hashes 
    during universe construction.
  * fix: rewrite the installation order to algorithm to distinguish 
    Pre-Depends from Depends and to provide better batching.
  * chore: temporarily disable Ubuntu packages builds due to 
    failing snapshot.ubuntu.com.
  * chore: new release.

 -- Alexey Naidyonov <alexey.naidyonov@gmail.com>  Thu, 09 Apr 2026 09:38:13 +0200

